"767","<TEXT>"
"768","77L New accounting pronouncement"
"769","In December 2011, the FASB issued ASU No. 2011 11 Disclosures"
"770","about Offsetting Assets and Liabilities. The update creates new"
"771","disclosure requirements requiring entities to disclose both"
"772","gross and net information for derivatives and other financial"
"773","instruments that are either off set in the Statement of assets"
"774","and liabilities or subject to an enforceable master netting"
"775","arrangement or similar agreement. The disclosure requirements"
"776","are effective for annual reporting periods beginning on or after"
"777","January 1, 2013 and interim periods within those annual periods."
"778","Putnam Management is currently evaluating the application of ASU"
"779","2011 11 and its impact, if any, on the funds financial"
"780","statements."
